  <h3><u><b>ABOUT US</b></u></h3>
  <br><p><i>Team Zindagi is a self-funded Non-Governmental Organization, established on 21st August 2021 by a small group of students in the town of Malbazar in Dooars, North Bengal. With time, work and effort our family is expanding with young minds full of innovative ideas. Our major areas of work includes protecting environment, helping to develop a healthy society, betterment of education for children, women empowerment and much more. In order to promote our local artists, every year Team Zindagi organizes Dooars Hip-hop Fest. We get to see many local young talents in our program.  

With the help of our team members and some self aware volunteers, we have conducted cleanliness drives, awareness camps, surveys on underprivileged child education, tree plantation drive, distribution of sweets and clothes, distributing sanitary pad and spreading general awareness on hygiene and health and more, in many parts of Dooars and we aspire to do more of it in future. 

If you are an environmentalist who believes that you can bring change in protecting the mother nature,  if you are a social activist who is strong enough to stand against the bias of society, if you think that underprivileged child's education can do much better than it's current situation and much more, then join us and be the part of the change. 

Come and join us, represent us as volunteers in the social activities and events. With your new and innovative ideas let's spread happiness wherever we go.
Let's make a change, let's be a change.</i></br></p>
